{
  "name": "design-playground",
  "version": "0.0.0",
  "private": true,
  "description": "Local-dev design playground. Its dependencies install NESTED under src/app/playground/node_modules (via setup.mjs) so the host project's package.json and lockfile are never touched. Local-dev only — never built in CI/prod. react/react-dom/next/tailwindcss are provided by the host (peerDependencies).",
